{
  "video_id": "LuA3xb-L8r8",
  "title": "How Does BitCoin Work?",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 3562.0,
      "end_time": 6395.0,
      "text": "(classical music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 9780.0,
      "end_time": 12111.0,
      "text": "- Hi, I'm Jonathan, this is Brain Stuff"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 12112.0,
      "end_time": 14725.0,
      "text": "and I've got some bad news for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 14725.0,
      "end_time": 16536.0,
      "text": "Money is imaginary."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 16536.0,
      "end_time": 19125.0,
      "text": "Now I don't mean that this printed piece of paper"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 19125.0,
      "end_time": 20740.0,
      "text": "is make believe."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 20740.0,
      "end_time": 23233.0,
      "text": "I can feel its texture and the ink even smudges off"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 23233.0,
      "end_time": 26672.0,
      "text": "on my fingers, but when you compare it to this other"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 26672.0,
      "end_time": 30910.0,
      "text": "piece of paper, what's really the difference?"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 30910.0,
      "end_time": 32427.0,
      "text": "Well one is a recognized currency"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 32427.0,
      "end_time": 34221.0,
      "text": "and the other isn't."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 34221.0,
      "end_time": 35379.0,
      "text": "And the reason why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 35380.0,
      "end_time": 38969.0,
      "text": "Well people agree that this piece of paper is a dollar"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 38969.0,
      "end_time": 40251.0,
      "text": "and has value."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 40251.0,
      "end_time": 42160.0,
      "text": "That's where money's worth comes from."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 42160.0,
      "end_time": 44108.0,
      "text": "We all pretend it's a currency."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 44108.0,
      "end_time": 47212.0,
      "text": "This is one reason why the digital currency Bitcoin"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 47213.0,
      "end_time": 48652.0,
      "text": "appeals to some people."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 48652.0,
      "end_time": 51250.0,
      "text": "See it's not tied to any political system"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 51250.0,
      "end_time": 53638.0,
      "text": "or government so it's not vulnerable to any of"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 53638.0,
      "end_time": 57552.0,
      "text": "their failings like the economic collapse in 2008."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 57552.0,
      "end_time": 60456.0,
      "text": "All it needs is for people to believe in it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 60456.0,
      "end_time": 63447.0,
      "text": "but lately well, some people are having a crisis"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 63447.0,
      "end_time": 64490.0,
      "text": "of faith."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 64489.00000000001,
      "end_time": 66298.0,
      "text": "That's why today on Brain Stuff we're going"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 66299.0,
      "end_time": 68861.0,
      "text": "to quickly establish some facts about Bitcoin"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 68861.0,
      "end_time": 71286.0,
      "text": "to better inform your beliefs about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 71286.0,
      "end_time": 73993.0,
      "text": "Now basically it's virtual money you can use"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 73993.0,
      "end_time": 77560.0,
      "text": "to buy and sell things online and it mimics real world"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 77560.0,
      "end_time": 80765.0,
      "text": "limited resources like gold for instance."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 80765.0,
      "end_time": 83978.0,
      "text": "It's also a cryptocurrency meaning that it's encrypted"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 83978.0,
      "end_time": 86210.0,
      "text": "in a way that prevents it from being copied."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 86210.0,
      "end_time": 89461.0,
      "text": "See every Bitcoin transaction is recorded"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 89461.0,
      "end_time": 91723.0,
      "text": "using a blockchain."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 91723.0,
      "end_time": 93328.0,
      "text": "Now that information acts like a ledger"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 93328.0,
      "end_time": 96276.0,
      "text": "that is encoded onto the Bitcoin itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 96276.0,
      "end_time": 98759.0,
      "text": "This prevents people from spending the same Bitcoin"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 98760.0,
      "end_time": 101680.0,
      "text": "more than once since everyone else on the currency's"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 101680.0,
      "end_time": 104929.0,
      "text": "peer to peer network knows that it just was spent."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 104930.0,
      "end_time": 107171.0,
      "text": "It's essentially just a number associated"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 107171.0,
      "end_time": 108646.0,
      "text": "with an internet address."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 108646.0,
      "end_time": 109912.0,
      "text": "You can store it on your phone"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 109912.0,
      "end_time": 112420.0,
      "text": "or a hard drive until it's used again."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 112420.0,
      "end_time": 115245.0,
      "text": "Now, here's some ways you could acquire Bitcoins."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 115245.0,
      "end_time": 117758.0,
      "text": "Accept them as payment for goods and services,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 117758.0,
      "end_time": 120521.0,
      "text": "exchange them for a more traditional form of currency,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 120522.0,
      "end_time": 122843.0,
      "text": "or you can mine them."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 122843.0,
      "end_time": 125642.0,
      "text": "That's right, like gold Bitcoins are mined."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 125642.0,
      "end_time": 128439.0,
      "text": "Not by old timing, grizzled prospectors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 128439.0,
      "end_time": 131781.0,
      "text": "but by powerful computers and like gold"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 131781.0,
      "end_time": 135990.0,
      "text": "the more people mine Bitcoins, the less there are"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 135990.0,
      "end_time": 137792.0,
      "text": "to be found, so they become harder to find."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 137792.0,
      "end_time": 139847.0,
      "text": "So instead of physically mining with a pick ax"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 139847.0,
      "end_time": 141898.0,
      "text": "you can attempt to solve math problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 141898.0,
      "end_time": 143215.0,
      "text": "with a computer."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 143215.0,
      "end_time": 147447.0,
      "text": "Imagine the problem is something like x + y = 15."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 147447.0,
      "end_time": 150253.0,
      "text": "Now if you can figure out what x and y are, congratulations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 150253.0,
      "end_time": 151516.0,
      "text": "you get a bitcoin."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 151516.0,
      "end_time": 154387.0,
      "text": "With little competition the problems are easier to solve"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 154388.0,
      "end_time": 158153.0,
      "text": "but when more people join the search you've got a race"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 158153.0,
      "end_time": 160780.0,
      "text": "and the problems get way more difficult,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 160780.0,
      "end_time": 163269.0,
      "text": "but as Bitcoin miners dwindle, the math problems will"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 163269.0,
      "end_time": 165870.0,
      "text": "get easier again to ensure the flow is steady,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 165870.0,
      "end_time": 169629.0,
      "text": "their value is boosted, and they remain inflation proof."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 169629.0,
      "end_time": 171631.0,
      "text": "Not all have been mined yet and we expect they won't be"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 171631.0,
      "end_time": 173131.0,
      "text": "until around 2140."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 174498.0,
      "end_time": 177420.0,
      "text": "So let's say you heard all this and thought"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 177420.0,
      "end_time": 180402.0,
      "text": "you know I want to grow up to be a professional Bitcoin"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 180402.0,
      "end_time": 181998.0,
      "text": "miner and trader."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 181998.0,
      "end_time": 183661.0,
      "text": "Well there are a few risks you should probably know"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 183661.0,
      "end_time": 185130.0,
      "text": "about first."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 185130.0,
      "end_time": 187783.0,
      "text": "For instance, because there's no regulatory agency"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 187783.0,
      "end_time": 191686.0,
      "text": "setting Bitcoin's value it tends to fluctuate wildly."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 191687.0,
      "end_time": 193761.0,
      "text": "Another Bitcoin problem is security."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 193761.0,
      "end_time": 196109.0,
      "text": "Now actually the format itself is fine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 196110.0,
      "end_time": 198533.0,
      "text": "but that doesn't protect it from hackers who target"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 198533.0,
      "end_time": 201274.0,
      "text": "the banks and exchanges that deal in Bitcoins."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 201275.0,
      "end_time": 203978.0,
      "text": "Again, this isn't the fault of the currency."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 203978.0,
      "end_time": 206418.0,
      "text": "If a bank were robbed, you wouldn't blame the dollar bill"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 206418.0,
      "end_time": 208369.0,
      "text": "for getting stolen right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 208369.0,
      "end_time": 211620.0,
      "text": "So Bitcoin has its slumps and for it to become"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 211620.0,
      "end_time": 214960.0,
      "text": "widely used its volatility needs to settle down"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 214960.0,
      "end_time": 215285.0,
      "text": "quite a bit."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 215285.0,
      "end_time": 217282.0,
      "text": "It's currently a high risk currency"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 217282.0,
      "end_time": 219680.0,
      "text": "that's totally unpredictable and we didn't even"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 219680.0,
      "end_time": 221827.0,
      "text": "get into the mysterious identity of Bitcoin's founder"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 221827.0,
      "end_time": 223572.0,
      "text": "Satoshi Nakamoto."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 223572.0,
      "end_time": 226664.0,
      "text": "Now personally I think the biggest drawback to Bitcoin"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 226664.0,
      "end_time": 229837.0,
      "text": "is that you just can't make it rain.."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 229837.0,
      "end_time": 232234.0,
      "text": "If you have experiences with Bitcoin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 232235.0,
      "end_time": 233420.0,
      "text": "let us know in the comments below."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 233420.0,
      "end_time": 235792.0,
      "text": "And let us know if there are any topics you'd like us"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 235793.0,
      "end_time": 236846.0,
      "text": "to cover."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 236846.0,
      "end_time": 239577.0,
      "text": "I actually have another pile of them right over there."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 239577.0,
      "end_time": 240815.0,
      "text": "Really, I mean it's just offscreen."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 240815.0,
      "end_time": 242762.0,
      "text": "So, the best part about this is I don't even have"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 242762.0,
      "end_time": 243665.0,
      "text": "to pick it up."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 243665.0,
      "end_time": 244537.0,
      "text": "We have interns to do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 244538.0,
      "end_time": 246121.0,
      "text": "See you guys later."
    }
  ]
